data.description: Affordable, Move-in Ready, Tri-level Home with instant SELLER's CONCESSIONS OF $5,000 for interest rate buydown! Welcome to your perfect starter home, designed to be energy-efficient and nestled on a spacious 0.18-acre fenced corner lot, conveniently situated near schools, parks, shopping & dining. This inviting residence offers 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. One of the standout features is a jetted bathtub, perfect for unwinding after a long day. The heart of the home is the kitchen, complete with all appliances and ample cabinet space. The main living area boasts vaulted ceilings, a bay window, hardwood floors and a gas fireplace - the perfect place for gathering with loved ones or relaxing in tranquility. The extra family room is perfect for a play room, or a private retreat. This home comes with a washer & dryer, a new HVAC system, lawn sprinkler system, mature landscaping, 2-car garage and additional RV/boat parking! Make your dreams of homeownership a reality in this inviting corner lot gem!
